      "name": "FDA pump hemolysis benchmark validation — 5-point operating map",
      "description": "CFD predictions of the relative hemolysis index compared against in-vitro measurements at five flow-speed operating points. All five points satisfy RH < 1. The associated UQ campaign (128 LHS runs) confirmed dominant sensitivity to tip clearance and inlet swirl; full sensitivity rankings and Sobol indices are tabulated in the validation report. Validation outcome: PASS at MRL 2 required level."
    },
