      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset provides full uncertainty budgets for all five operating points. Fluid temperature held at 37 ± 0.5 °C; hematocrit 33 ± 1%. Boundary conditions in CFD set to experimental nominal values; parametric sweeps within measurement uncertainty performed as part of the UQ campaign. Level 2 achieved."
