      "rationale": "Normalized error E% ranges from 3.1% to 11.7% across the five operating points. Validation uncertainty intervals overlap at all points. The UQ sensitivity analysis confirmed that prediction spread attributable to input uncertainty is within the experimental scatter band. Level 2 achieved."
