      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry as the COU device. Reynolds number and flow coefficient at all five operating points are within 8% of COU nominal conditions. Blood analog fluid properties match within viscosity uncertainty. Level 2 achieved."
