      "rationale": "At MRL 2, numerical solver error beyond discretization error is scoped to level 1 (awareness). Residual convergence criteria are enforced in the solver settings and monitored in post-processing scripts, but no formal iterative error quantification beyond standard convergence monitoring was performed. Acceptable at MRL 2."
