      "rationale": "At MRL 2, test sample characterization is required only at level 1. The FDA benchmark uses a single manufactured pump specimen; manufacturing variability was not formally characterised in the experimental dataset. Acceptable at MRL 2; geometric variability was instead explored computationally in the UQ campaign."
